{
  "texts": [
    "The scheme is examined by evaluating its operating performance using the PoW, PoS and PoA consensus mechanisms.",
    "All examinations are conducted on real patient EMRs.",
    "The performance results of the proposed scheme show that PoW provides the best results in terms of block size, memory usage, and number of operations for both sensitive and non-sensitive patient data.",
    "The proposed scheme ensures the storage, access, and sharing of medical data without risking security vulnerabilities and attacks.",
    "It also ensures that patients are the owners of their data."
  ]
}